760
00:36:38,379 --> 00:36:39,939
in the throne room of heaven,

761
00:36:39,939 --> 00:36:43,019
we see the throne, we see the four and 20 elders,

762
00:36:43,019 --> 00:36:44,819
we see these four beasts,

763
00:36:44,819 --> 00:36:47,059
but we notice tonight what they're saying.

764
00:36:48,019 --> 00:36:50,219
And I hope that we would examine our own lives.

765
00:36:50,219 --> 00:36:51,499
What are we saying?

766
00:36:51,499 --> 00:36:53,499
What are we talking about?

767
00:36:53,499 --> 00:36:56,699
Are we offering the praise of our lips to our God?

768
00:36:56,699 --> 00:36:57,619
Continually?

769
00:36:57,619 --> 00:36:59,099
Are we praising him?

770
00:36:59,099 --> 00:37:00,339
Are we thanking him?

771
00:37:00,339 --> 00:37:02,859
We're talking about how great he is.

772
00:37:02,859 --> 00:37:05,459
I mean, when you think something is great,

773
00:37:05,459 --> 00:37:06,379
you talk about it.

774
00:37:07,459 --> 00:37:08,699
Amen?

775
00:37:08,699 --> 00:37:12,979
If you've had a great meal, you talk about it.

776
00:37:12,979 --> 00:37:15,179
A great experience, you talk about it.

777
00:37:16,539 --> 00:37:18,819
Our God surpasses all of that.

778
00:37:19,819 --> 00:37:21,379
All of it.

779
00:37:21,379 --> 00:37:23,339
We ought to be talking about him, amen?

780
00:37:23,339 --> 00:37:24,939
He is king of kings and Lord of lords.

781
00:37:24,939 --> 00:37:27,619
He is the great, he is the Lord God Almighty,

782
00:37:27,619 --> 00:37:29,139
the great I am.

783
00:37:29,139 --> 00:37:33,419
And it is our job, our responsibility and our privilege

784
00:37:33,419 --> 00:37:37,579
to talk about him, to lift up his name and praise him.

785
00:37:37,579 --> 00:37:38,419
Let's pray together.

786
00:37:38,419 --> 00:37:39,499
Father, we love you.

787
00:37:39,499 --> 00:37:40,619
We thank you for loving us.

788
00:37:40,619 --> 00:37:42,019
We thank you for the privilege

789
00:37:42,019 --> 00:37:43,659
of being able to study your word.

790
00:37:44,779 --> 00:37:48,099
God, as we seek to make some application in our lives tonight

791
00:37:48,099 --> 00:37:49,939
from this passage of scripture

792
00:37:49,939 --> 00:37:54,939
and we see the challenge has been brought before us.

793
00:37:55,939 --> 00:38:00,539
And God, I thank you for challenging my heart.

794
00:38:01,939 --> 00:38:03,779
Lord, I pray that you would help us

795
00:38:03,779 --> 00:38:07,379
to speak the things that we ought to speak.

796
00:38:10,499 --> 00:38:14,979
That we would learn from this portion of scripture,

797
00:38:14,979 --> 00:38:17,739
not only how these four beasts are described,

798
00:38:17,739 --> 00:38:20,779
but Lord, that we'd be greatly impacted

799
00:38:20,779 --> 00:38:22,099
by what they're doing.

800
00:38:22,939 --> 00:38:25,539
Help us to examine our own lives.

801
00:38:25,539 --> 00:38:30,539
Help us this week to say the things that we ought to say,

802
00:38:30,539 --> 00:38:31,899
to speak of thee.

803
00:38:32,939 --> 00:38:37,579
Lord, help others around us to know how great you are,

804
00:38:38,939 --> 00:38:43,779
how powerful you are, how holy and righteous you are,

805
00:38:43,779 --> 00:38:48,699
because we've opened our mouth and we've praised your name.

806
00:38:48,699 --> 00:38:51,899
Would you move and work in these moments as only you can

807
00:38:52,539 --> 00:38:53,859
we'll give you the honor and glory

808
00:38:53,859 --> 00:38:56,059
for it's in Christ's name we pray, we just.

